      <title>塞尔维亚在政治动荡和全球价格风险中维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/serbia-holds-rates-amid-political-turmoil-and-global-price-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀率居高不下且政治动荡和全球贸易紧张局势导致该国面临更多价格风险，塞尔维亚连续第五个月维持借贷成本不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/serbia-holds-rates-amid-political-turmoil-and-global-price-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 11:01:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀加剧导致美国债券价格上涨，创 12 月以来最差表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-bonds-rise-after-hot-inflation-fuels-worst-day-since-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债在经历了去年 12 月以来的最大抛售后小幅走高，因为投资者等待最新的通胀快照，以便从周三高于预期的通胀数据中寻找美国利率走势的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-bonds-rise-after-hot-inflation-fuels-worst-day-since-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:59:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DoubleLine 询问微软债务是否比美国国债更安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/doubleline-asks-whether-microsoft-debt-is-safer-than-treasuries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司的市值比大多数国家股市的总和还要大，其债券评级让许多国家羡慕不已。现在，DoubleLine Capital 的一位投资组合经理提出了一个令人不安的、尽管是理论上的问题，即这家软件制造商及其资产负债表：它比美国政府的资产负债表更安全吗？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/doubleline-asks-whether-microsoft-debt-is-safer-than-treasuries</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>创纪录的股市“脆弱性”向大盘发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/record-stock-fragility-sends-warning-to-broader-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国一些最大股票的不稳定性不断上升，导致个股“脆弱性”达到创纪录水平，市场越来越容易受到股票集群波动的影响，就像 1990 年代后期互联网泡沫时期那样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/record-stock-fragility-sends-warning-to-broader-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
