    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦由黄金支持的 ZiG 错过了黄金创纪录的涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/-usd-zwg-zimbabwe-s-bullion-backed-zig-is-missing-out-on-gold-s-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于流动性紧缩导致经济受阻，且难以将津巴布韦货币兑换成美元，津巴布韦以黄金为支撑的货币错失了金价大幅上涨的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/-usd-zwg-zimbabwe-s-bullion-backed-zig-is-missing-out-on-gold-s-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:19:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡考虑采取税收优惠措施以振兴股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/singapore-moots-tax-incentives-to-revive-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由新加坡政府牵头的审查小组提议采取税收激励措施来重振股市，这是在流动性低下和新股上市稀缺的市场中采取的第一步措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/singapore-moots-tax-incentives-to-revive-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:02:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>神秘的对冲基金重写了 4.5 万亿美元产业的规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/how-secretive-hedge-fund-qrt-hit-the-big-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[许多金融界最聪明的人在试图闯入对冲基金贵族阶层时都失败了。QRT 从默默无闻迅速崛起为前 1% 的行业领导者，正在改写未来的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/how-secretive-hedge-fund-qrt-hit-the-big-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 05:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普“令人震惊”的贸易局势令印尼寻求新协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/indonesia-seeks-new-deals-as-shocking-trump-tariffs-roil-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼贸易部副部长迪亚·罗罗·埃斯蒂·维迪亚·普特里表示，随着全球保护主义愈演愈烈，印尼正寻求实现市场多元化，同时也采取措施保护本土制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/indonesia-seeks-new-deals-as-shocking-trump-tariffs-roil-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 02:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
